        <h2>GAIA-X &ndash; Federated Data Infrastructure</h2>
        <img src="images/logo-gaia-x.png" class="logo-gaia-x" alt="GAIA-X logo" title="GAIA-X" />
        <p class="lead">
	  On the digital summit 2019 in Dortmund, the
          <a href="https://www.data-infrastructure.eu/">GAIA-X project</a>
	  was launched by the german ministry of economic affairs and energy (BMWi). The goal 
	  of <a href="https://www.data-infrastructure.eu/">GAIA-X</a> is the defintion and the
	  setup of a secure and trustworthy data infrastructure for Europe. One of the defining
	  properties of the targeted solution is the usage of open technologies.
        </p>
        <blockquote style="margin-top: 50px">
          A strong open infrastructure ecosystem is the foundation of digital sovereignty.
          <span>Quelle: &bdquo;GAIA-X: Technical Architecture (Release – June, 2020)&ldquo;</span>
        </blockquote>
