          The team around director Rafael Laguna de la Vera provides comprehensive support for inventors:
          SPRIND arranges financing, helps to find a founding team and creates connections to other experts
          from science and industry. People with groundbreaking ideas, proven expertise and passion are
          gathered at SPRIND.
        </p>
        <p class="lead">
          One of the first projects supported by SPRIND is the "Sovereign Cloud Stack" project.
        </p>
        <p class="lead">
          SPRIND is not only constantly looking for new, groundbreaking ideas, but is also expanding its
          network of experts. Further information is available at <a href="https://sprind.org/en">sprind.org</a>.
